### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:3000/users

### Get contact by id
GET http://localhost:3000/users/59b99db4cfa9a34dcd7885b6

### Create contact
POST http://localhost:3000/users HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "firstName":"Ashley",
    "lastName":"Weaver",
    "email":"aWeaver@test.com",
    "favoriteColor":"Brown",
    "birthday":"06/19/2000"
}

